Review the changes, fixes, and more in each version of Elasticsearch.

To check for security updates, go to [Security announcements for the Elastic stack](https://discuss.elastic.co/c/announcements/security-announcements/31).

parts.content:
You can find the release notes for different versions of Elasticsearch on the official documentation site. Here is a direct link to the release notes where you can review the changes, fixes, and enhancements for each version:

- [Elasticsearch Release Notes](https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/current/es-release-notes.html)

This page includes detailed information about features, enhancements, fixes, security updates, and more for each released version of Elasticsearch.
